            . (police-constable S 24). I took the prisoner; she said the tongs belonged to her mistress, but not the blanket; I found this cap in her pocket.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I had had the blanket in my box for four months before I went to her house; I had put the tongs in there because I had wetted them, and put them there till I could clean them.</p>
